testcase.name: Login_into_application.
testcase.system-out: ✅ Given I am on the WestwingNow home page✅ When I search for "möbel"✅ Then I should see product listing page with a list of products✅ When I click on wishlist icon of the first found product✅ Then I should see the login and registration overlay✅ When I switch to login form of the overlay ✅ And I log in with existing credentials✅ Then the product should be added to the wishlist✅ And I go to the wishlist page✅ And I delete the product from my wishlist
